  "body": "There are a few changes in `specs/phase0/beacon-chain.md` that aren't reflected in the diff/summary that is `specs/phase0/altair.md`, e.g.\r\n\r\n- `process_eth1_data_reset` is not marked `# [New in Altair]` in `process_epoch`, and its definition isn't inlined\r\n- `process_effective_balance_updates` not marked new, not inlined\r\n- `process_slashings_reset` not marked new, not inlined\r\n- `process_randao_mixes_reset` not marked new, not inlined\r\n- `process_historical_roots_update` not marked new, not inlined\r\n\r\n(As of v1.1.0-alpha.1)",
