    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "the idea was to refactor in phase 0 so that we can more easily edit `process_epoch` moving forward as we change sub-sections of `process_epoch` or add additional epoch-level functionality.\r\n\r\nthe comments about `modified`/`new` in altair are meant to describe the state of the spec relative to the current phase 0 spec. given that we already made the refactor into subroutines in the current phase 0 spec, i'd say the items you listed do not need any of these comments (unless something is actually new that has been missed...) so we can close this issue\r\n\r\ndoes that make sense or am i misunderstanding?",
